<p>Syntax to display file date:</p>

<pre class="js_code_quote box_code">&lt;module&gt;
{
	"GetFile":
	{
		"fileName": "redaxscript.zip",
		"type": "date"
	}
}
&lt;/module&gt;</pre>

<p>Syntax to display file size:</p>

<pre class="js_code_quote box_code">&lt;module&gt;
{
	"GetFile":
	{
		"fileName": "redaxscript.zip",
		"type": "size",
		"unit": "mb"
	}
}
&lt;/module&gt;</pre>